data.description:
Welcome to 2213 Hickory Grove Trail, where modern elegance meets Texas charm!! Nestled in the heart of Fort Worth, this stunning residence invites you into a world of comfort and style. Discover spacious living areas adorned with exquisite details, from gleaming granite counter tops to designer fixtures throughout. The gourmet kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances for a haven for culinary enthusiasts.
The outdoor living spaces are equally impressive, with a covered patio that extends the living area outdoors. Perfect for enjoying a quiet evening, the patio overlooks a professionally landscaped backyard. Located in a family-friendly neighborhood, this property is more than an address; it's a community. Conveniently situated near schools, parks, and major thoroughfares, your Texas dream life is just a doorstep away. Don't miss your chance to own a slice of Fort Worth's charm. Welcome home!
